    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《美丽的光》是一款激烈的<strong>PvPvP撤离型射击游戏</strong>，由独立工作室<strong>Deep Worlds</strong>开发。踏入逼真的游戏世界，作为快速反应部队的成员不断成长，或者作为异形怪物干扰其他玩家的突袭行动。《光芒行动》通过惊艳的视觉效果，突显<strong>沉浸式的恐怖和战术玩法</strong>。游戏旨在通过刺激的体验和陡峭的学习曲线推动玩家突破极限，考验玩家的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进入、夺取、撤离</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// 进入</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f1db52b904ce7d0ca38c6fb62b125742.poster.avif?t=1770044782\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f1db52b904ce7d0ca38c6fb62b125742.webm?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f1db52b904ce7d0ca38c6fb62b125742.mp4?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备面对干预区，搜寻神秘神石，或完成你的任务。装备各种各样的武器、防护和装置，并与两名同伴组成小队。在充满传说、障碍和危险的恶劣环境中着陆和探索。敌对干员和怪物异形会穷尽一切办法干掉你们。每次突袭都是独一无二的，因此，请做好面对未知的准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// 夺取</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f98664d8ca2ef21359afc0a856aad694.poster.avif?t=1770044782\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f98664d8ca2ef21359afc0a856aad694.webm?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/f98664d8ca2ef21359afc0a856aad694.mp4?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有神石均有不同的属性可供开发。在这个满目疮痍的世界，这些资源的开发决定着一座城市的生死。因此，神石十分珍贵，而你们需要率先夺取神石，并消灭一切阻碍势力，不论是人是鬼。如果神石已经被人取走，那就确保你们才是把它带回家的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// 撤离</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/40fc181934a754ac5b5e2111669e0c9b.poster.avif?t=1770044782\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/40fc181934a754ac5b5e2111669e0c9b.webm?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/40fc181934a754ac5b5e2111669e0c9b.mp4?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦死亡，则意味着任务失败，并会失去你所携带的一切物品。发射信号弹，召集撤离直升机，在被杀之前逃离——不论是否取得神石。毕竟，有时候你的生命要比一块奇怪的石头——或是某个朋友——更加宝贵。在撤离载具到达前坚持住，并防范任何其他潜在的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// 推进</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/34e6a6414d4101cb0a6fbd4f16adc8b9.poster.avif?t=1770044782\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/34e6a6414d4101cb0a6fbd4f16adc8b9.webm?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/34e6a6414d4101cb0a6fbd4f16adc8b9.mp4?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若要推动进度，你需要完成任务、夺取神石并成功逃生。商人等待着你完成他们的差事——实现他们的期望，就能获得奖励。在类似RPG的进度树上合理花费你的奖励，从而升级你的角色和改进你的技能，或者向商人购买武器和珍贵装备，为下一次突袭行动做准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// 玩异常并猎杀玩家</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/667423595595908480f2d212332cac65.poster.avif?t=1770044782\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/667423595595908480f2d212332cac65.webm?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313230/extras/667423595595908480f2d212332cac65.mp4?t=1770044782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为异常体，你的目标是猎杀并吞噬玩家，阻止他们带着神器逃脱。释放异常体，尽可能多地吞噬玩家以获取经验。提升你的技能，获得更多能力，并解锁新的怪物异常体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抢先体验版功能：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 主要<strong>非对称</strong>游戏模式：<strong>突袭</strong>。参与24人比赛，其中包括6个分别由3名干员组成的小队以及6个被称为异形的怪物，然后努力夺取神石或杀死所有人类。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 深度、战术、硬核FPS机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 打造极致的<strong>沉浸式体验</strong>和<strong>压迫性氛围</strong>（逼真的呼吸声、脚步声、心跳声、防毒面具等）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 灵感源于军方界面设计的<strong>剧情内平视显示器</strong>（前臂个人数字助理）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 由玩家社区主持和自定义的<strong>自托管或专用服务器</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 高级物品栏系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 战术装备：激光器、战术灯、夜视镜……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 详细地图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 我们注重流畅性和问题修复：当然，bug难免会发生，但我们始终致力于清除bug，让大家在良好帧率环境下运行游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>完整版功能：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 雇佣兵和合约系统，可发布或完成多项任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 全面的团队系统，包含统计数据、排行榜、级别、角色、管理和奖励生成器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 更多内容（枪械、装置、外观、异形）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 更多地图——扩大《光芒行动》的末日后剧院范围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 秘密探险游戏模式。</p></li></ul>",
